params.tokensToRedeem: the amount of nTokens to convert to cash

params.tokensToRedeem: the amount of nTokens to convert to cash

returns.newifCashAssets: an array of fCash asset residuals to place into the account
returns.totalPrimeCash: positive amount of asset cash to the account
